io.github.eutro.jwasm

Class ModuleWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.eutro.jwasm.BaseVisitor<ModuleVisitor>
      • io.github.eutro.jwasm.ModuleVisitor
        • io.github.eutro.jwasm.ModuleWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ByteArrayConvertible

    public class ModuleWriter
extends ModuleVisitor
implements ByteArrayConvertible
    A ModuleVisitor that generates the corresponding WebAssembly bytecode as it is visited. This can be retrieved using toByteArray() after BaseVisitor.visitEnd().
